  "body": "### What is wrong?\r\n\r\nWe're currently running the sync processes (i.e. `FullNodeSyncer` and `LightChain`) directly in trinity, together with the `PeerPool` required for them to work.\r\n\r\n### How can it be fixed\r\n\r\nWe should teach `p2p.Server` how to select the appropriate sync service and then use just `p2p.Server` in trinity, as it takes care of setting up and running the `PeerPool` and the server that accepts incoming peer connections",
